<div class="container">
    <h1>FAQs</h1>
    
    <div class="faq-item">
        <h3>How do I create a new blog post?</h3>
        <p>To create a new blog post, log in to your account, navigate to the dashboard, and click on the "New Post" button. Use the rich text editor to write your content, add images and other media, and format your post. When you're ready, click "Publish" to make your post live.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
        <h3>Can I schedule my posts for future publication?</h3>
        <p>Yes, you can schedule your posts for future publication. After writing your post, click on the "Schedule" button, select the desired date and time, and your post will be published automatically at that time.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
        <h3>How do I manage categories and tags?</h3>
        <p>You can manage categories and tags from the dashboard. Go to the "Categories" or "Tags" section, where you can create new categories and tags, edit existing ones, and assign them to your posts to help organize your content.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
        <h3>What customization options are available for my blog's appearance?</h3>
        <p>Our blog web application offers a variety of customizable themes. You can choose a pre-designed theme or customize colors, fonts, and layouts to match your brandâ€™s aesthetic. Navigate to the "Themes" section in your dashboard to start personalizing your blog.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
        <h3>How do I improve the SEO of my blog posts?</h3>
        <p>To improve the SEO of your blog posts, you can customize meta titles, descriptions, and keywords for each post. Use our built-in SEO analysis tool to check the optimization of your content and follow the suggestions to enhance your SEO performance.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
        <h3>Can I integrate social media with my blog?</h3>
        <p>Yes, you can integrate social media with your blog. You can add social sharing buttons to your posts, making it easy for readers to share your content on various social media platforms. Additionally, you can share your posts directly from the dashboard.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
        <h3>How do I enable and manage comments on my posts?</h3>
        <p>Comments can be enabled or disabled from the post settings. To manage comments, go to the "Comments" section in your dashboard, where you can approve, delete, or reply to comments. You can also set up comment moderation settings to control who can post comments.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
        <h3>Is there an analytics dashboard to track my blog's performance?</h3>
        <p>Yes, our blog web application includes a comprehensive analytics dashboard. You can track key metrics such as page views, unique visitors, and engagement rates. Use these insights to understand your audience better and refine your content strategy.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
        <h3>How do I secure my blog and data?</h3>
        <p>Your blog and data are secured with advanced security measures, including SSL encryption. We also perform regular backups to ensure your data is safe from unauthorized access and data loss. You can manage security settings from the "Security" section in your dashboard.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
        <h3>Can I collaborate with other authors on my blog?</h3>
        <p>Yes, you can collaborate with other authors using the multi-author support feature. You can assign different roles and permissions to authors, editors, and admins, allowing you to effectively manage your content team.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
        <h3>How do I set up a newsletter subscription?</h3>
        <p>To set up a newsletter subscription, go to the "Newsletter" section in your dashboard. Here, you can create and customize subscription forms to collect email addresses from your visitors. You can then send out regular updates, new posts, and special announcements to your subscribers.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
        <h3>Is there a mobile app available for managing my blog?</h3>
        <p>Yes, we offer a mobile app that allows you to write and publish posts, moderate comments, and track analytics directly from your smartphone or tablet. The mobile app ensures you stay connected with your blog on the go.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
        <h3>What should I do if I encounter a technical issue?</h3>
        <p>If you encounter a technical issue, please visit our support page or contact our customer support team. We are here to help you resolve any issues as quickly as possible to ensure your blogging experience is seamless.</p>
    </div>
</div>
